title: Wahoo's
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Fast food, Take-out, Mexican, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. A surf-themed tacos & Mexican fast food chain. The menu includes different filling choices for tacos, burritos, enchiladas, and bowls. Veg filling include marinated tofu, saute mixed vegetable teriyaki, or vegetarian rice and bean(with cheese). Vegans must specify; otherwise you might get cheese/dairy in your order.
